<tmc-service-inc>
<pub id="RM0251U">
<servcat id="30">
<name>ENGINE</name>
<section id="10008_S000H" variety="S000H">
<name>2GR-FE EMISSION CONTROL</name>
<ttl id="10008_S000H_7306P_T00EJ" variety="T00EJ">
<name>VACUUM SWITCHING VALVE (for EVAP)</name>
<para id="RM000002BNM000X" category="A" type-id="80001" name-id="EC0TF-01" from="200601">
<name>REMOVAL</name>
<subpara id="RM000002BNM000X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000002BNM000X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00006SI00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE V-BANK COVER SUB-ASSEMBLY
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Hold the front of the V-bank cover and raise it to disengage the 2 clips on the front of the cover. Continue to raise the cover to disengage the clip on the rear of the cover and remove the cover.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A132968" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Attempting to disengage both front and rear clips at the same time may cause the cover to break.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000002BNM000X_01_0002" proc-id="RM0250U___0000BSY00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE NO. 1 VACUUM SWITCHING VALVE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Disconnect the 2 vacuum hoses and No. 1 vacuum switching valve connector.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A132952E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the bolt and No. 1 vacuum switching valve.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A132953" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
</pub>
</tmc-service-inc>